QuestData.Title: Between a Saurok and a Hard Place
QuestData.Description: Dear $p,$b$bWe have received your research on the saurok and believe we have pieced together clues about their past.$b$bIf you visit us at the Seat of Knowledge in Vale of Eternal Blossoms we can add this contribution to your personal collection.$b$bThank you for your diligence!$b$bSincerely,$b$bLorewalker Cho
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring Between a Saurok and a Hard Place to Lorewalker Cho.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Lorewalker Cho at the Seat of Knowledge in Vale of Eternal Blossoms.
